com.apaulin.http.rpc

Class ShowConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.apaulin.http.rpc.RPCRequest
      • com.apaulin.http.rpc.GetSchema
        • com.apaulin.http.rpc.ShowConfig

  • public class ShowConfig
extends GetSchema
    Retrieves a compact string representation of the configuration
    Since:
    13/07/2018
    Version:
    0.1 The path param is a keypath to the configuration to be returned. result_as controls the output format, string for a compact string format and json for json. max_size sets the maximum size of the data field in kb, set to 0 to disable the limit.
    Author:
    Anthony Paulin
